oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Application of dynamic material model for hot isostatic pressing of powder compacts
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: MURTY, SVSN
RAO, BN
KASHYAP, BP
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: behavior
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The derivation of efficiency of power dissipation for PM compacts is presented. An accurate evaluation of the efficiency parameter for any now stress data is described and demonstrated using the test data of PM Rene 95 alloy. PM/0894.
